  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "body": "Warden Poon was the warden of the ${link_0} near the ${link_1}. He was known to be a tough, insulting warden who bore little to no respect for the criminals under his watch. He especially despised ${link_2} ${link_3}, because he was a traitor to the ${link_4}. He saw Iroh as nothing more than a weak, washed-up, lazy, and wretched old man content to grovel in his own filth. Warden Poon spent most of his days walking up and down the prison corridors and verbally assaulting the prisoners in order to break their spirits.",
